  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nForks have been introduced into the gossipsub topics. We need the eth2-libp2p service to know about the current fork and when a new fork happens, unsubscribes from current gossip topics and re-subscribes. \r\n\r\nThis change requires the libp2p service to modify gossip messages from various parts of lighthouse to ensure they are sent on the correct topic",
